{"tid":1553152,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[緊急文宣] 有義工想將所有影片加字幕，","createTime":"2019-09-08T13:45:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T16:48:52.000Z","uid":259493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c11719db43367e016023b4e460bc3fd096949681","tid":1553152,"uid":259493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:45:42.000Z","msg":"代一位朋友轉載：<br />\n<br />\n&quot;有沒有人在連登有帳戶？我不能有，查出來我執業證也隨時沒了。我要問是因為，我有很多外國朋友想知道香港的情況。我做了兩個Youtube的Playlist（等一下發出來），但很多都沒有英文字幕。我已經發電郵問了港台和明周，說我可以免費幫忙做字幕，但他們不一定答應。我想在連登post一下，問問做文宣的可以怎麼幫忙做英文字幕。我覺得這些Youtube對讓外國人（比如那些議員）理解香港發生什麼事有幫助。任何的幫忙都先謝謝<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我認識不少在華盛頓的律師朋友，他們很高級，都認識政界的</span></span></strong>&ldquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLZUlp4gARXfKaP2V9hA7HuTOBteH8KFgg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fplaylist%3Flist%3DPLZUlp4gARXfKaP2V9hA7HuTOBteH8KFgg&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2Bv2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=4d4afb2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLZUlp4gARXfKaP2V9hA7HuTOBteH8KFgg</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLZUlp4gARXfIehteazhtMyfztwqXKZ8_j\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fplaylist%3Flist%3DPLZUlp4gARXfIehteazhtMyfztwqXKZ8_j&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2Bv2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=55d84df9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLZUlp4gARXfIehteazhtMyfztwqXKZ8_j</a>"},{"pid":"fb89cd0f71fead2f58b7abf0c30b009b9c66809d","tid":1553152,"uid":112816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:47:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9e498e829107429d91f39774a743f30eb7f93206","tid":1553152,"uid":274141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:51:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8aaea80c5cabe015a6410ca084715d0ee7073e7c","tid":1553152,"uid":259493,"like":0,"dislike